  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Place the slices of bread on a baking sheet and toast in the oven for 2 minutes.",
    "Remove the bread from the oven and brush with melted butter.",
    "Sprinkle smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper on top of the bread.",
    "Aerate the narutomaki using a food processor or hand mixer until it becomes light and airy.",
    "Top each slice of bread with a piece of aerated narutomaki.",
    "Sprinkle shredded cheddar cheese and chopped scallions on top of the narutomaki.",
    "Place the baking sheet back in the oven and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly."
